275
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:34,440
Aku bukan anak kecil, brengsek!

276
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:37,640
Oh, sial. Kita bunuh saja mereka.

277
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:40,120
Jagalah sikapmu dan jangan memaki.

278
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:48,160
Halo.

279
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:52,160
Persetan denganmu, tengik!

280
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:56,280
Jangan pernah menyuruhku!

282
