395
00:30:50,030 --> 00:30:54,030
Arahkan ke dadanya.

396
00:31:27,430 --> 00:31:29,950
Apa yang kau lakukan padaku?

397
00:31:29,950 --> 00:31:33,950
Jessica?

398
00:31:40,510 --> 00:31:43,710
Kau...

399
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:44,910
